cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "RateXp: Drop-in feedback collection for agentic skills"
message: "If you use RateXp, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Hikmet
    family-names: Beyoglu
    email: hikmet.beyoglu@hotmail.com
repository-code: "https://github.com/HikmetB1/RateXp"
url: "https://github.com/HikmetB1/RateXp"
abstract: >-
  RateXp is a feedback collection solution for agentic skills. A skill author
  adds a couple of lines to their SKILL.md and it asks users for a rating and,
  with consent, the full conversation, redacts personal information, and shows
  the results on a live dashboard.
keywords:
  - agentic skills
  - feedback
  - dashboard
  - LLM
  - evaluation
